title: Wild Card Weekend Preview
itunes:title: Wild Card Weekend Preview
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- dive deep into the four games on Wild Card Weekend and make their picks. Plus, quick reaction to Doug Marrone's surprising departure from the Buffalo Bills.
